OL,3,CSudan militia leader convicted by the
OL,4,CICC of war crimes during Darfur war
OL,6,FThe International Criminal Court has
OL,7,Fconvicted a leader of the Janjaweed
OL,8,Fmilitia of playing a leading role in a
OL,9,Fcampaign of atrocities committed in
OL,10,Fthe Sudanese region of Darfur more
OL,11,Fthan 20 years ago.
OL,13,FIt was the first time the court had
OL,14,Fconvicted a suspect of crimes in
OL,15,FDarfur.
OL,17,FThe court ruled that the atrocities,
OL,18,Fincluding mass murders and rapes, were
OL,19,Fpart of government plans to violently
OL,20,Fsnuff out a rebellion in the western
OL,21,Fregion of Sudan.
