OL,3,CSudan militia leader convicted by the
OL,4,CICC of war crimes during Darfur war
OL,6,FAli Muhammad Ali Abd-Al-Rahman, also
OL,7,Fknown as Ali Kushayb, attended the
OL,8,Fcourt wearing a suit and tie.
OL,10,FListening through a headset, he showed
OL,11,Fno emotion as Presiding Judge Joanna
OL,12,FKorner read out 27 guilty verdicts. He
OL,13,Fwill be sentenced at a later date and
OL,14,Ffaces a maximum life sentence.
