OL,3,CSudan militia leader convicted by the
OL,4,CICC of war crimes during Darfur war
OL,6,FThe verdict comes as allegations of
OL,7,Fatrocities and famine continue to
OL,8,Femerge from Sudan. In July, the ICC's
OL,9,Fdeputy prosecutor told the United
OL,10,FNations that war crimes and crimes
OL,11,Fagainst humanity are continuing to
OL,12,Ftake place in Sudan's vast western
OL,13,FDarfur region, where civil war has
OL,14,Fraged for more than two years.
