OL,3,CSudan militia leader convicted by the
OL,4,CICC of war crimes during Darfur war
OL,6,FProsecutors say that Abd`Al-Rahman was
OL,7,Fa senior commander in the Janjaweed
OL,8,Fmilitias during the Darfur conflict
OL,9,Fthat erupted when rebels from the
OL,10,Fterritory's ethnic central and sub-
OL,11,FSaharan African community launched an
OL,12,Finsurgency in 2003, complaining of
OL,13,Foppression by the Arab-dominated
OL,14,Fgovernment in the capital, Khartoum.
OL,16,FThen-president Omar al-Bashir's
OL,17,Fgovernment responded with a scorched-
OL,18,Fearth campaign of aerial bombings and
OL,19,Fraids by the Janjaweed, who often
OL,20,Fattacked at dawn, sweeping into
OL,21,Fvillages on horseback or camelback.
