OL,3,CSudan militia leader convicted by the
OL,4,CICC of war crimes during Darfur war
OL,6,FThe campaign included mass killings
OL,7,Fand rapes, torture and persecution. Up
OL,8,Fto 300,000 people were killed and 2.7
OL,9,Fmillion were driven from their homes
OL,10,Fin Darfur. Al-Bashir has been charged
OL,11,Fby the ICC with crimes including
OL,12,Fgenocide, but he has not been handed
OL,13,Fover to face justice in The Hague.
