OL,4,CICC of war crimes during Darfur war
OL,6,FAs the verdicts are announced in The
OL,7,FHague, conflict continues in Sudan
OL,8,Fbetween the paramilitary Rapid Support
OL,9,FForces and Sudan's military.
OL,11,FTensions erupted in 2023 between the
OL,12,Ftwo previous allies that were meant to
OL,13,Foversee a democratic transition after
OL,14,Fa 2019 uprising.
