OL,6,FThe fighting has killed at least
OL,7,F40,000 people, according to the World
OL,8,FHealth Organisation, and displaced as
OL,9,Fmany as 12 million others. More than
OL,10,F24 million people are facing acute
OL,11,Ffood insecurity in Sudan, according to
OL,12,Fthe World Food Program.
OL,14,FTwo decades ago, the RSF was born out
OL,15,Fof the Janjaweed militias, and
OL,16,FJanjaweed groups still help the RSF.
